title: Storybud
overview: The most watched RTÉ show to feature people sitting in a yellow chair, is back for yet another series. Newcomers Amy Huberman, Kayleigh Trappe, Demi Isaac Oviawe and Carl Mullan join Storybud veterans Jason Byrne and Tara Lynne O'Neill to regale us with ‘totally true' stories about celebrities, aliens, mysterious football boots and dinosaurs.
